<div id="homepage" :class="[heroHeightSet ? '' : 'uninitialized']" v-cloak>
  <div class="hero d-flex flex-column justify-content-center" full-page-hero>
    <div class="container text-center">
      <img src="/images/bitclaims-logo.png"/>
      <h1 class="text-muted">Be cool. <span class="text-secondary">Crowdsource your healthcare.</span></h1>
      <div>
        <div class="more-info-text text-info" @click="clickHeroButton()">
          <div class="text">Learn more</div>
          <div class="icon">&darr;</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="about-wrapper bg-dark" role="scroll-destination">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about text-center">
        <h3>Take charge of your healthcare costs.</h3>
        <p>BitClaims provides a platform that is powered by smart contracts and blockchain technology so that patients and providers can connect directly in a trustless, secure and compliant way.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="features text-center">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="feature col-sm">
            <div class="icon bg-info">
              <i class="fa fa-handshake-o"></i>
            </div>
            <h4>Form Buyer's Club</h4>
            <p>Gather a group of people to crowdsource their halthcare plans, which includes primary care, elective care, and cosmetic care</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm feature">
            <div class="icon bg-primary">
              <i class="fa fa-heart"></i>
            </div>
            <h4>Request Service</h4>
            <p>All parties in the BitClaims network will know the terms of the deal and no one will be able to change the rules or permission around the deal at any time unless a concensus is reached</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm feature">
            <div class="icon bg-danger">
              <i class="fa fa-list-ul"></i>
            </div>
            <h4>Authorize Payment</h4>
            <p>Providers are compensated according to their performance as the funds are secured in a smart contract until called upon via a public/private key ceremony that both parties must sign off on</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a class="btn btn-outline-success mt-5" href="/signup">Join now</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="more-info-wrapper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h3>What is a BitClaim?</h3>
        <p>The BitClaims core business functions that enables donators to become members of a participant group which holds BitClaims that are tied to the direct cash flow of the BitClaims platform. To find out more on what BitClaims are and how to participate, please contact us.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<%- /* Expose locals as `window.SAILS_LOCALS` :: */ exposeLocalsToBrowser() %>
